=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_Latoocarfian2DC_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright clean sound, with square_like oscillator character around 1903 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1902.7314
  harmonic_decay_rate: -6.7153
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9997
  pitch_clarity: 20.7694
  inharmonicity: 0.0085
  type: square_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -32.0074
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

